item.dc:creator: @valcombird valcombird
item.description:
@valcombird wrote:

[quote=“Team_Rocket, post:6, topic:450206”][quote author=valcombird link=topic=553106.msg4052668#msg4052668 date=1342665071]

Before you say it’s a leech… Please check the forums and see what I have done…

We are only 5 days old as of 7/18/2012!

Why not just post the Development Log here so we can all see it? I’m curious as to how much work you’ve done in 5 days.

Well let me gather up all the forums posts…

Er… Nevermind forgot I had a changelog.txt o.O…

By the way, your Co-Owner’s post makes me not want to play. I just read through your updates, and ummm… Mostly just small bug fixes and what-not. There’s really nothing major or redone from what I saw, correct me if I’m wrong though. What base is this by the way? Soulsplit?

Yea… Co-Owner… The topic about the funny pictures? Asked him why it was there…

And no not soulsplit. Sadly its insidiaxv2… Most of the server features were already in there… Not a leech just wanted a challenge I hear insidiaX is very hard to get stable and fix so I wanted to step up and do it. But I will be revamping most of it… Whenever I get less distracted… Two laptops really make its hard to stay on one topic… But thanks for actually taking notice in the server.
[/quote]

Thank you for being honest about the features. I started our Devolution 7.0 source, because I was looking to have fun instead of a challenge. We’re having a ton of fun working on it so far. You’re welcome, just stay motivated, and try to make original content and write as much as you can by yourself.[/quote]

I will don’t worry :).

Also BUMP! Updates for 7/18/2012 have been posted!
